Operationalise data science on your business data using UnifyML SQL with zero coding skillsets needed. UnifyML.com is a data science product which aims to provide unified data science approach in operationalising machine learning and Ai using SQL.

It reduces operational cost, improves efficiency and gets value from your data within minutes and not days. It's has got modern micro service architecture for scalability with SQL and open jdbc interface to run dataPrep, predictive, clustering, classification, timeSeries and many more algorithms at Scale.

Please visit and check the site www.unifyml.com for more details.
